{"tid":1664883,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"除左救護，唔好再讓路、清RB比消防","createTime":"2019-10-20T10:37:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-21T02:02:35.000Z","uid":79589,"like":20,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"a98ab703623483ce39afed69427f5802f8bf526e","tid":1664883,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:37:46.000Z","msg":"發夢見到大量港島消防車係到鳩行<br />\n<br />\n單係4點幾時旺角到就見到上環、堅尼地城嘅消防，但附近完全冇火，班消防都冇意欲落車<br />\n<br />\n家陣消防出車目的好明顯就係比班狗叫去開路、消RB<br />\n<br />\n班狗之後就可以快速推進<br />\n<br />\nSet RB 火魔法都係阻狗推進，點解要比消防再入？"},{"pid":"8581fada783f34ccb433fd445e010bf04f33a640","tid":1664883,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:38:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"553a09bab8ba236854cbdbc420df63e65b7c7ecc","tid":1664883,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"救護A360 載狗"},{"pid":"7b6590af8a97f2d8453cebf7e05fce6b72013e59","tid":1664883,"uid":79589,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"553a09bab8ba236854cbdbc420df63e65b7c7ecc","tid":1664883,"uid":222970,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:38:33.000Z","msg":"救護A360 載狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:39:30.000Z","msg":"救護好難避免，真心"},{"pid":"1a3de445e9c67b00bcda15af7a6c02e91fe6d102","tid":1664883,"uid":5801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"消防真係無必要都唔使再讓 又幾何真係現場需要出動救人<br />\n同埋好似話今日班狗已經哩埋係消防車後面等捉人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c05034b3df03f99995744f9d94f132bc50c4dff","tid":1664883,"uid":79589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1a3de445e9c67b00bcda15af7a6c02e91fe6d102","tid":1664883,"uid":5801,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:41:57.000Z","msg":"消防真係無必要都唔使再讓 又幾何真係現場需要出動救人<br />\n同埋好似話今日班狗已經哩埋係消防車後面等捉人 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-20T10:52:25.000Z","